div.p:
In ſhort, do not talk and make a noiſe to get a name of forward men, but do the thing, bee conſtant in ſecret duties, and act Religion in your callings, for it is not a name or notion, it is a frame of nature, and an habit of living by Divine Rule; what it is you will then know when you have it in truth firſt, and in power next, and not before. Onely this for the preſent, it is that you muſt live and dye by, that you muſt riſe and reign by; therefore my Children I

give you that advice which I gave your Brother, now with God;
Tho. H. bee more than you ſeem, do more than you talk of in point of Religion; ſatisfie your own conſciences in what you do, all men you ſhall never ſatisfie, nay, ſome will not bee ſatisfied, though they bee convinced.
